{"tid":1717464,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"我大膽一言，中大只係七一重現版","createTime":"2019-11-13T15:17:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-13T23:43:58.000Z","uid":126889,"like":14,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a7a306c2ce46fc692b359f666730f568b3b09aa7","tid":1717464,"uid":126889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T15:17:32.000Z","msg":"記唔記得7.1 點贏? 焦土+撤退<br />\n<br />\n沙盤推演返 如果好似7.1 咁處理<br />\n<br />\n1. 對家叫緊陣 彩佢有味 保存實力 經驗同裝備<br />\n<br />\n2. 唔好冇士氣咁退 有士氣咁走 <br />\n<br />\n3. 除文物典籍等不能取代既野 一律焦左佢<br />\n<br />\n4. 建立組織 依家留返係中大既都較可信<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n歡迎各大冷氣軍師 brain storm 下"},{"pid":"ff694ae0a5bb22407318339deebe89fb04b34412","tid":1717464,"uid":126889,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T15:20:09.000Z","msg":"5. 唔記得左 撤出後立即立援手足開花"},{"pid":"b5e3753f5926e66ce7385a5a0b59a9648fcfa471","tid":1717464,"uid":126889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T15:23:12.000Z","msg":"真係冇人諗下?"},{"pid":"947cfcbf46dd42b0ea44421067ffa8db7f9ebc26","tid":1717464,"uid":126889,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T15:25:12.000Z","msg":"但不排除 此思路已經比對家計算在內"},{"pid":"c14c4b7032cc00996bc0ca5afaa7ed0b33895284","tid":1717464,"uid":126889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T15:33:24.000Z","msg":"我非散水黨 但不得不考慮既係 開實彈要點守 <br />\n除非有大炮等武器鎮守<br />\n對家到現今為止武器射程都係100米左近 出左m16 既就唔同講法<br />\n就算整得切土製武器都未必夠打<br />\n<br />\n7.27 8.13 抗爭者係受fake news影響驚住咁走 但7.1 係主動計劃下走的"},{"pid":"46d34b1fc5c892293c2a540e3a6b4372a41ac050","tid":1717464,"uid":74642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T15:33:46.000Z","msg":"1999"},{"pid":"0d2bda0da4c27a0747e25c35189c1929566eeb80","tid":1717464,"uid":126889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"46d34b1fc5c892293c2a540e3a6b4372a41ac050","tid":1717464,"uid":74642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T1